    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 97.</p><p>Tier I: Elemental Awakening</p><p>Primordial Element. When you gain this Heroic Feat, choose one of the following damage types: acid, cold, fire, lightning, or thunder. This is your Primordial Element.</p><p>Elemental Attunement. You gain immunity to your Primordial Element. Your spells and class features that deal damage of your Primordial Element ignore resistance, and treat immunity as if it were resistance.</p></div>",
